#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.1:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Sekhabalavagga "
msgstr "1. Powers of a Trainee "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: sekhabalasaṅkhittasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Saṅkhittasutta "
msgstr "1. In Brief "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.1, sc1
msgctxt "an5.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an5.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

msgctxt "an5.1:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "an5.1:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.1:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "an5.1:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: sekhabalāni → sekkhabalāni (mr)
msgctxt "an5.1:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcimāni, bhikkhave, sekhabalāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these five powers of a trainee. "

msgctxt "an5.1:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

#. VAR: hirībalaṃ → hiribalaṃ (bj, s3, pts1)
#. VAR: vīriyabalaṃ → viriyabalaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.1:2.3"
msgid "Saddhābalaṃ, hirībalaṃ, ottappabalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, paññābalaṃ—"
msgstr "The powers of faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an5.1:2.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca sekhabalāni. "
msgstr "These are the five powers of a trainee. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.1:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: "
msgstr "So you should train like this: "

msgctxt "an5.1:3.2"
msgid "‘saddhābalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalena, hirībalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalena, ottappabalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalena, vīriyabalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalena, paññābalena samannāgatā bhavissāma sekhabalenā’ti. "
msgstr "‘We will have the trainee’s powers of faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom.’ "

msgctxt "an5.1:3.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how you should train.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.1:3.4"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "an5.1:3.5"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.1:3.6"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
